text: Volmer Thomsen (31 October 1917 - 28 October 2000) was a Danish gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Horsens
